com.flowpowered.react.collision.broadphase

Class SweepAndPruneAlgorithm

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.flowpowered.react.collision.broadphase.BroadPhaseAlgorithm
      • com.flowpowered.react.collision.broadphase.SweepAndPruneAlgorithm

  • public class SweepAndPruneAlgorithm
extends BroadPhaseAlgorithm
    This class implements the Sweep-And-Prune (SAP) broad-phase collision detection algorithm. This class implements an array-based version of the algorithm from Pierre Terdiman that is described here: www.codercorner.com/SAP.pdf.
